io Santiago Bernabeu]]\n|attendance=70,000\n|referee=Manuel Diaz Vega\n|result=W\n}}\n\n==UEFA Cup==\n{{main|1991\u201392 UEFA Cup}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=18 September 1991\n|time=\n|team1=[[\u0160K Slovan Bratislava|Slovan Bratislava]] {{flagicon|TCH}}\n|score=1\u20132\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=1991/matches/round=630/match=4528/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report] \n|team2={{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n|goals1=[[Peter Dubovsk\u00fd (footballer)|Dubovsk\u00fd]] {{goal|69}}\n|goals2=[[M\u00edchel (footballer)|M\u00edchel]] {{goal|13|pen.}}<br />[[Emilio Butrague\u00f1o|Butrague\u00f1o]] {{goal|78}}\n|stadium=[[Bratislava]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W\n }}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=18 September 1991\n|time=\n|team1=[[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]] {{flagicon|ESP}}\n|score=1\u20131\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=1991/matches/round=630/match=4529/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report] \n|team2={{flagicon|TCH}} [[\u0160K Slovan Bratislava|Slovan Bratislava]]\n|goals1=[[Alfonso P\u00e9rez|Alfonso]] {{goal|41}}\n|goals2=[[\u013dudov\u00edt Lancz|Lancz]] {{goal|89}}\n|stadium=[[Madrid]]\n|attendance=20,000\n|referee= \n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=23 October 1991\n|time=\n|team1=[[FC Utrecht|Utrecht]] {{flagicon|NED}}\n|score=1\u20133\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=1991/matches/round=631/match=4690/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report] \n|team2={{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n|goals1=[[W\u0142odzimierz Smolarek|Smolarek]] {{goal|18}}\n|goals2=[[Robert Prosine\u010dki|Prosine\u010dki]] {{goal|44}}<br />[[Robert Roest|Roest]] {{goal|72|o.g.}}<br />[[Francisco Villarroya|Villarroya]] {{goal|80}}\n|stadium=[[Stadion Galgenwaard|Stadion Nieuw Galgenwaard]], [[Utrecht]]\n|attendance=20,000\n|referee=[[Lajos N\u00e9meth]] ([[Hungarian Football Federation|Hungary]]) \n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=6 November 