ke]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[1999\u20132000 UEFA Champions League|1999\u201300]]\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[M\u00e1rio Jardel]]\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[FC Porto|Porto]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" align=center|10\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Rivaldo]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ra\u00fal (footballer)|Ra\u00fal]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n|-\n|[[2000\u201301 UEFA Champions League|2000\u201301]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ra\u00fal (footballer)|Ra\u00fal]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n|align=center|7\n|-\n|[[2001\u201302 UEFA Champions League|2001\u201302]]\n|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Ruud van Nistelrooy]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|align=center|10\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303 UEFA Champions League|2002\u201303]]\n|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Ruud van Nistelrooy]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|align=center|12\n|-\n|[[2003\u201304 UEFA Champions League|2003\u201304]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Fernando Morientes]]\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]\n|align=center|9\n|-\n|[[2004\u201305 UEFA Champions League|2004\u201305]]\n|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Ruud van Nistelrooy]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|align=center|8\n|-\n|[[2005\u201306 UEFA Champions League|2005\u201306]]\n|{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Andriy Shevchenko]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[A.C. Milan|Milan]]\n|align=center|9\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 UEFA Champions League|2006\u201307]]\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Kak\u00e1]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[A.C. Milan|Milan]]\n|align=center|10\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 UEFA Champions League|2007\u201308]]\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|align=center|8\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League|2008\u201309]]\n|{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Lionel Messi]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n|align=center|9\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310